{
  "stem": "893.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a full train, full of farmers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we sort of had a low profile, kept a low profile, and no one bothered us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In fact, they offered us food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we arrived, I think, after a 12-hour journey, we arrived to that train station, Obisovce, where he arranged, with a-- on a wagon, we were taken to that remote village off the main road, and off the main railroads.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We came there to one of the farmers, and we told them that we-- we want-- we are-- we would like-- we want to enter hiding, because we don't want the Germans to take us along, whether as laborers or as fighters.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At that time, there was-- the Slovakian army revolted against the Germans, and they were crushed right away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the government was still pro-Nazi.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a good excuse, especially to simple farm people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they suggested that we go into hiding instead of staying, because the German army-- or the German SS people, sometimes they came into the village just to be sure that some Russian partisans are not hiding out there.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They came to raid the village, and they left the people alone, but just to be sure that partisans-- because there were partisans who were blowing up bridges and disrupting communications.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this was a good place to hide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was a time when they were there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That we should go into hiding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We-- And they were afraid that if we-- if they are caught with some people who don't belong to the village, then they'll be-- they might harm them, also.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they took us to one of the hiding places.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was a log house on a mountainside in the forest, deep in the forest.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
